{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_10_02",
  "title": "井川葵 2話 いいパフォーマンスが出来た理由",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "話は分かった。……けど、今の話の中に\n俺の質問への答えは、なかったと思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand the story… but\nI don’t think you gave me an answer to my question.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、忘れてた。そういえばトリエルとのバトルで\nあの曲をうまく出来た理由だったっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I forgot. It was about the reason I could perform that song well‚\nin the battle with TRINITYAiLE‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 17.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん説明するつもりだったよ。この話には\n続きがあるんだ。時間も遅いし、帰りながら話すよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I planned to explain. This story has\nmore to it. It’s late‚ so I’ll tell you on the way back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今、「忘れてた」って言ったよな？\n……まぁいい。続きを聞かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just said‚ “I forgot‚” didn’t you?\n…Well‚ okay. Tell me the rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『Grab the BIG4』開催中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—During “Grab the BIG4”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 34.7000058492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "驚いたな……あれから数日しか経ってないのに\n新曲の振り付け、だいぶ出来上がってるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m surprised… only a few days have passed‚ yet—\nThe new choreography is already quite developed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けを作ったり、個人練習をするくらいしか\nやることがないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s not much I can do except work on choreography\nand practice on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "僕は活動休止中の身だからね\n……振り付けは四人分出来てるけど、見てみる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m on a hiatus‚ after all.\n…I’ve finished the choreography for all four members. Want to see it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、もちろんだ。ぜひ見せてくれ\n……それにしても、安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ of course. Show me.\n…Still‚ I’m relieved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.100004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "今の僕を見て、よく安心出来るね。あ、もしかして\n僕がやる気をなくして、ゴロゴロしてると思ってた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re relieved to see me now? Ah‚ could it be…\nyou thought I’d lost motivation and was just lazing around?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.900004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃない。葵は練習も振り付けも好きだって\n知ってるから、そんなことは心配してないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not it. I know you love both practice and choreography‚\nso I wasn’t worried about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺が安心したのは、四人分の振り付けを作ってたことだ\nそれって、リズノワを辞めるつもりはないってことだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What reassured me was that you’d made choreography for all four.\nThat means you don’t intend to leave LizNoir‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "……別に。他にやることがないからね\n気分転換にやってるだけだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Not really. I just had nothing else to do.\nI’m just doing it for a change of pace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6666714986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "大体、こんなに調子を落としてる僕が\nいつリズノワに戻れるかなんて、分からない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ with the way I am right now‚\nI have no idea when I’ll be able to return to LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん達は\nいつでも戻って来てほしいと思ってるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san and the others\nprobably want you back whenever you’re ready‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "うん。莉央達なら、今のこんな僕でも歓迎してくれる\nそれは僕にだって分かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Even someone like me now‚ they’d welcome me.\nI know that much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3333381653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、みんなの優しさに甘えて、今戻ってしまったら\n僕が僕を許せなくなるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if I let their kindness sway me and return now—\nI wouldn’t forgive myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9666714986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて偉そうなことを言ってるけど\nスランプ脱出の目処は全然ついてないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I sound arrogant‚ but\nI haven’t found a way out of this slump at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.800004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "今の僕が、この振り付けで踊っても\n納得のいくものには全然ならないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I danced this choreography right now‚\nit wouldn’t be satisfying at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.000004832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今作ってるこの振り付け自体\nもっといいものに出来るはずなんだ。なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And this choreography I’m making now\ncould be even better. Yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.5333432515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……葵、一つ提案なんだが\nその振り付け、莉央さんに見せてみたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Aoi‚ I have a suggestion.\nWhy not show the choreography to Rio-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.0333432515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんなら、もっといいものにするために\n意見を出してくれるんじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She might give advice\nto improve it further.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.7000221252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "え……でも自分の都合でリズノワから離れた僕が\nそんなことをするのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… but I left LizNoir for my own reasons‚\nso I shouldn’t do that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1333554585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんにどう思われるか、気になるのか？\nそんなことを気にするなんて、葵らしくないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You care about what Rio-san would think‚ huh?\nThat’s not like you‚ Aoi‚ to worry about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6333554585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだよ、僕らしくないって\n僕はこう見えて結構気配りの人なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What do you mean “not like me”?\nI’m actually quite considerate to others‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8666887919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ははっ、それはすまなかったな\nでも、いい振り付けにしたいんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ sorry about that.\nBut you want it to be good‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.2666887919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そのためなら他人の顔色なんて気にしない\n自分のやりたいことをやるのが井川葵じゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about what others think for that.\nDoing what you want— isn’t that exactly who Aoi Igawa is?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.6000221252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "……知った風なことを言われるのは好きじゃないけど\n{user}君の言う通りだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don’t like being spoken to as if you know everything‚\nbut you’re right‚ {user}-kun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.0000221252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "似合わないことを言っちゃったね。面と向かって言って\nくれてありがとう。後で録画して、莉央に送ってみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said something unlike me. Thank you for saying it to my face.\nI’ll record it and send it to Rio later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.3666887919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 214.7500249226
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 214.7500249226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、そんな話もしたな。その後は聞いてないけど\n莉央さんから返事はあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ we talked about that too. I haven’t heard what happened next.\nDid Rio-san reply?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.3228498249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "うん、あった。そしてそれが、君が知りたがってた\n理由だよ。……あれ、もしかして通じてない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ she did. And that’s the reason\nyou wanted to know. …Wait‚ you don’t get it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.0000221252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 234.3000249226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』のセミファイナルで\nいいパフォーマンスが出来た理由なんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason we could perform so well\nin the “Grab the BIG4” semifinals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.0000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（理由……ど、どういうことだ？）\n（葵の言ってることが全然分からない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The reason… w-what does that mean?）\n（I have no idea what Aoi is talking about…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.1666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 247.233358256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "僕の言ってること、全然分からないって顔してるね\n仕方ないな。じゃあ説明してあげる。特別にね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look like you don’t understand what I’m saying.\nFine. I’ll explain it. Just for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.9333554585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "あの日、君のアドバイスを受けて\n振り付けの映像を莉央に送ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That day‚ I took your advice‚\nand sent the choreography video to Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.9333595275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 263.4666956583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "莉央は、何も聞かずに振り付けのアップデートに\n付き合ってくれたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio didn’t ask any questions and just helped\nupdate the choreography.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.3333595275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "そうして完成した振り付けを、莉央は愛とこころにも\n共有して、セミファイナルまでに完璧にマスターした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then she shared the completed choreography with Ai and Kokoro‚\nand they all mastered it perfectly by the semifinals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.4666697184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 277.7666956583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』の決勝トーナメント\n直前にか？　そんな忙しい時期に、どうして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right before the “Grab the BIG4” final tournament?\nDuring such a busy time… why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.0666928608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "三人とも、僕が必ず戻って来ると信じてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All three believed I would definitely return.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.2666956583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 285.2666956583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "そして僕が戻って来たら\nすぐにでもこの曲をやれるように、練習してくれていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And they practiced\nso we could perform this song immediately when I returned.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.9333595275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 297.0000350951
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "だからぶっつけ本番でも、振り付けは完璧だったんだ\nまぁ、多分だけどね。直接聞いた訳じゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why even on the first try‚ the choreography was perfect.\nWell‚ probably. I didn’t hear it directly‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.5666928608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 306.6333684284
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな。でも、葵にとって大切なことだろ？\nちゃんと確認しておいた方がいいんじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. But it’s important to you‚ isn’t it?\nYou should make sure about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.1000261942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_02-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫。口に出さなくても分かるさ\n――だって僕達は、LizNoirだからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine. I understand even without words.\n—Because we’re LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.4333595275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
